{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0d54959fac","title":"准备夺取充州及聊城博平","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2441a3a0b9","index":0,"year":1946,"month":6,"day":18,"articleId":"0d54959fac"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji21","name":"毛泽东全集第21卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji21.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji21":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"99c94f778f","type":"paragraph","text":"准备夺取充州及聊城博平口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"0d54959fac"},{"id":"68e0617a2d","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年6月18日）陈、舒，刘、邓、薄（一）对夺取兖州及聊博两战役，望在本月内准备完毕，但在未得中央最后电令前，不要实行攻击。（二）最近我已得了许多地方，目前短时期内需要平静一下。（三）如蒋方于十五日期满后重新发动向东北进攻，或大举攻我苏北，你们便可夺取充州、聊、博。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"0d54959fac"},{"id":"67783e3ae2","type":"paragraph","text":"中央","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"0d54959fac"},{"id":"39b853c8c8","type":"paragraph","text":"已巧[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央起草的给新四军军长第山东军区司令员陈毅、政治部主任舒同和香算普豫军区司令员刘伯系、政治委员邓小平、第一副政治委员薄一波的电报。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"0d54959fac"}],"page":{"id":"ee876e2022","publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"0d54959fac","start":392,"end":392}}}},"__N_SSG":true}